		   <tr><td class="headerrow" colspan="2" class="mform" valign="top" id="forumSubject">Soloing Post-50 ?!?<br clear="all" /><script type="text/javascript">document.title = document.title + ": Thread: Soloing Post-50 ?!?";</script>
		   <span class="sm">Posted @ Sun, Jan 18th 3:37 PM2004 </span><span id="notbold">| <span class="sm">IP: Logged</span> | <a href="/db/classes.html?class=9&mid=107445818669555&post=1"><a class="sm" href="/db/classes.html?class=9&mid=107445818669555&post=1&replyto=107445818669555"><img src="/shared/reply_to_thread_ico.gif" border="0" alt="Reply..." height="11" width="17" /> Reply to this</a></a>    <a name=107445818669555></a></small></td></tr>
		   <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform" ><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=222944"><span id=>chitan</span></a><b><span id=></span></b><br />4 posts
		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=chitan&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>Heya, all!<br><br>My now 51 shaman is my prime char, so I dont have any previous experience with any other classes or zones at this level.&nbsp;&nbsp;I discovered soloing about level 35 or so, and been loving it ever since.<br><br>Anyone have suggestions for zones (or even specific strategies) where I can SOLO for the next 15 levels?  I am mostly interested in maximizing XP and leveling, tho decent loot is never refused.<br>=-)<br><br>Thanks for any and all suggestions!<br><br>~Taerri Erwin<br>&quot;purty&quot; troll Mystic of 51 years on Tunare</p></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >1 Replies</td></tr></table>
